# Jabber::GroupChat::GotMsg --
#
#       Just got a group chat message. Fill in message in existing dialog.
#       If no dialog, make a freash one.
#       
# Arguments:
#       body        the text message.
#       args        ?-key value? pairs
#       
# Results:
